	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Kaiga Atomic Power Station&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;is a nuclear power station in Karnataka.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Rajasthan Atomic Power Station&lt;/strong&gt; is&amp;nbsp;a nuclear power station&amp;nbsp;located at Rawatbhata in Rajasthan.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Narora Atomic Power Station&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;is a nuclear power station located in Uttar Pradesh.&lt;/li&gt;
